REQUIRES:
JQuery 1.5.1



DESCRIPTION:
A very simple carousel plugin

<div id='my-carousel'>
	<ul>
		<li>Item 1</li>
		<li>Item 2</li>
		....
		<li>Item N</li>
	</ul>
</div>


<script>
	$('#my-carousel').carousel({width:400,duration:1000,delay:5000});
</script>

PARAMETERS:
width - width of the slides to be shown
duration - how long to animate each slides transition
delay - how long to wait between transitions
timer - if you want to be able to manipulate the interval then you'll need to pass in a reference


ADVICE:
play
abuse
improve